# deployment-toolkit
Multi-Tenant Deployment Automation (Gitea Actions)
"This repository contains the automation engine I built to manage deployments across 90+ unique healthcare environments.

Key Challenges Solved:

Resource Optimization: Engineered CI/CD pipelines to run on constrained hardware by utilizing specialized Docker Buildx configurations.

Scalability: Simplified the migration and provisioning of PostGIS databases using idempotent Bash scripts.

Reliability: Implemented 'Fail-Fast' logic and string parsing to ensure zero-downtime migrations."
